lemma IsBinomialRandom.inf (hG : IsBinomialRandom G p P) (hY : IsBinomialRandom H q P) :
    IsBinomialRandom (fun ω => G ω ⊓ H ω) (p * q) P where
  map_eq := sorry
  aemeasurable := sorry
```

We need to complete the proof for `AEMeasurable (fun ω => G ω ⊓ H ω) P`.

```tactics
variable (G p P) in
lemma isAEMeasurable_inter : AEMeasurable (fun ω => G ω ⊓ H ω) P := by
  apply AEMeasurable.inter
  exact hG.aemeasurable
  exact hY.aemeasurable
```

